netInt

Class GraphPad

  • java.lang.Object
    • processing.core.PApplet
      • netInt.GraphPad
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    processing.core.PConstants

    public class GraphPad
extends processing.core.PApplet
    This is the central class of NetInt. It inherits from Processing.PApplet thus it encloses all the functionalities of a Processing sketch. It could be instantiated in three ways. The simplest way is to invoke GraphPad() to launch a visualization pad together with a Control Panel and a Console Catcher. The second way is to invoke GraphPad("filePath") parameterizing the file path. It launches the visualization pad but omits launching the Control Panel. The last way is to run the included main class. The latter needs to set the graph path inside the body of the main method
    Version:
    alpha
    Author:
    jsalam
